Deck The Hall Ball

Key Arena
Seattle Center, WA


107.7 The End [KNDD-FM] presents Deck the Hall Ball '98: Hole, Garbage, Soul Coughing, Cherry Poppin' Daddies, Cake, Mark Lanegan and Elliott Smith. 
6:30 PM start, runs till midnight, tix $31.50, with 11,000 expected.


Lisa Jann, Seattle Times Reporter, 12/4/98: Hole: On leave from Hollywood, Courtney Love returns to her old stomping grounds to strut her band's new, high-gloss finish. With "Celebrity Skin" confounding old fans and recruiting new, this Seattle appearance should be a preview of what's to come with Hole's 1999 headline tour.
